---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="about" description="About Kevin Jones">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <p>
    I'm Kevin — an indie systems builder. I work mostly in Python, write a
    fair amount of TypeScript, and reach for whatever else fits the job.
    Lately that's been LangGraph supervisors, prediction-market bots, and
    the occasional 3D printer firmware hack.
  </p>

  <p>
    I like small tools that compose. I like reverse-engineering proprietary
    protocols when the open path doesn't exist yet. I like building
    something end-to-end on a weekend rather than designing a perfect
    abstraction across six.
  </p>

  <h2>What I'm interested in</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Multi-agent LLM orchestration — supervisors, delegation, durable state</li>
    <li>Quantitative trading on novel venues (prediction markets, options, paper)</li>
    <li>Browser automation and headless control via Chrome DevTools Protocol</li>
    <li>Hardware-adjacent software — 3D printers, microcontrollers, voice interfaces</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Get in touch</h2>
  <p>
    <a href="mailto:kevinmjones@gmail.com">kevinmjones@gmail.com</a> ·
    <a href="https://github.com/kevinmjones">github.com/kevinmjones</a>
  </p>
</Layout>
